{
  "stem": "8786.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But this is just a little character of his, because he was-- he knew-- he knew what he wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He knew what he wanted to say, and he had a very strong character, and a beautiful way of expressing himself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Probably this was helping him in this situation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my town, we had about 170, 180 Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was still a young boy, and it was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had much less then what today's children have or demand, but people were happy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The community life was happy because everybody knew everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still believe in that in a small town you have more [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] closeness to people than in a big town.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As far as the-- well, naturally, we heard already the 19-- early '30s, we heard already what's going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And many, many times, non-Jewish boys used to warn us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They'd say, hey, listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Hitler is coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Hitler is coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Unfortunately, we didn't realize that this is not-- it wasn't just an empty threat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not only we as children-- we took it-- we didn't-- it didn't even bother us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was such a natural thing that the Jewish boy went out on the street-- he could wind up with a stone thrown into his head.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was a natural thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I went to a school, high school, with Gentile boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were on a good term, that-- but there was always-- we had-- they always-- we had to-- they made us feel always that we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And most of the best students were Jewish boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And it wasn't a long time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it wasn't-- so the time period, what I would call my childhood, was a short one.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
